archimate:DataObject.name: Identity Data 2
archimate:DataObject.documentation: The set of data associated with an Identity that permits identification of the underlying Entity. In Self-Sovereign Identity, the sharing of Identity Data is under the control of the Identity Owner. See also Sovrin Identity Data. See Appendix A.
